title: WEDNESDAY 1/20 - Aaron Rodgers having fun
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 1/20 - Aaron Rodgers having fun
description:
As we get set for Championship weekend we have some injury updates for Patrick Mahomes (0:15) and Antonio Brown (0:44). Packers QB Aaron Rodgers one win away from the Super Bowl and says he's having the time of his life (1:29). We'll have the latest on coaching and general manager moves from around the league. Plus, Sarah Thomas ready to make Super Bowl history (4:16)
